ows 200|IOW]]'''<br><small>28</small>\n|\n| style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Messina Wildlife Animal Stopper 200|IRP]]<br><small>4</small>\n|\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Berlin ARCA 200|BLN]]<br><small>9</small>\n| style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Allen Crowe Memorial 100|ISF]]<br><small>22</small>\n|\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Kentuckiana Ford Dealers Fall Classic|SLM]]<br><small>8</small>\n| style=\"background:#FFFFFF;\"| [[Southern Illinois 100|DSF]]<br><small>C</small>\n| colspan=2|\n! rowspan=2| 3rd\n! rowspan=2| 4735\n! rowspan=2| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racing-reference.info/drivdet/poolebr01/2012/A|title=Brennan Poole \u2013 2012 ARCA Racing Series Results|work=Racing-Reference|accessdate=February 3, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=2| [[Toyota]]\n|\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Mobile ARCA 200|MOB]]<br><small>7</small>\n| colspan=4|\n| style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| '''[[Pocono ARCA 200|POC]]'''<br><small>1*</small>\n| style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[RainEater Wiper Blades 200|MCH]]<br><small>11*</small>\n|\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[The All-American Race Weekend|NJE]]<br><small>6</small>\n|\n| style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Ansell ActivArmr 150|CHI]]<br><small>2</small>\n|\n| style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| '''[[Pennsylvania ARCA 125|POC]]'''<br><small>2*</small>\n| colspan=2|\n| style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Herr's Live Life with Flavor 200|MAD]]<br><small>10</small>\n| colspan=2|\n| style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Kansas Lottery 98.9|KAN]]<br><small>4</small>\n|-\n! rowspan=4| [[2013 ARCA Racing Series|2013]]\n! 15\n| [[Lucas Oil 200 (ARCA)|DAY]]\n| [[ARCA Mobile 200|MOB]]\n| [[Kentuckiana Ford Dealers 200|SLM]]\n| [[International Motorsports Hall of Fame 250|TAL]]\n| [[Menards 200|TOL]]\n| [[Akona 250|ELK]]\n| [[Pocono ARCA 200|POC]]\n| style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[Patriot Pumps 200|MCH]]<br><small>1</small>\n| [[SCOTT 160|ROA]]\n| colspan=7|\n| style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[Southern Illinois 100|DSF]]<br><